      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! Super clean, smoke-free, and meticulously cared for. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how gorgeous it is. Shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
